### Test Candidate Profile API

# Get candidate profile by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/candidate/profile/{{candidate_id}}

# Example with a specific candidate ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/candidate/profile/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

# Test with invalid ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/candidate/profile/

# Test with non-existent ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/candidate/profile/99999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999

